    {
      "text": "Which of the following statements is correct regarding indirect ophthalmoscopy?",
      "choices": [
        {
          "id": 0,
          "text": "The image is erect and real."
        },
        {
          "id": 1,
          "text": "The condenser lens needs to be kept close to the eye."
        },
        {
          "id": 2,
          "text": "It provides 15x magnification."
        },
        {
          "id": 3,
          "text": "It provides 3-5x magnification."
        }
      ],
      "correct_choice_id": 3,
      "solution": "<ul>\n\t<li>Indirect <span class=\"customMeta\" data-dictid=\"5e1068918f16927771941f59541497\">ophthalmoscopy</span> is a technique used for examining the <span class=\"customMeta\" data-dictid=\"f17d8978bd1692777197621051012f\">retina</span> and other structures in the <span class=\"customMeta\" data-dictid=\"a5c6cb079d16927771967e62ffee72\">posterior</span> segment of the eye.</li>\n\t<li>It provides 3-5x magnification.</li>\n</ul>\n\n<p><br />\n </p>\n\n<table cellspacing=\"0\" style=\"border-collapse:collapse; width:624px\">\n\t<tbody>\n\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid #000000; border-left:1px solid #000000; border-right:1px solid #000000; border-top:1px solid #000000; vertical-align:top\">\n\t\t\t<p><strong>Characteristic</strong></p>\n\t\t\t</td>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid #000000; border-left:1px solid #000000; border-right:1px solid #000000; border-top:1px solid #000000; vertical-align:top\">\n\t\t\t<p><strong>Direct Ophthalmoscopy</strong></p>\n\t\t\t</td>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid #000000; border-left:1px solid #000000; border-right:1px solid #000000; border-top:1px solid #000000; vertical-align:top\">\n\t\t\t<p><strong>Indirect Ophthalmoscopy</strong></p>\n\t\t\t</td>\n\t\t</tr>\n\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid #000000; border-left:1px solid #000000; border-right:1px solid #000000; border-top:1px solid #000000; vertical-align:top\">\n\t\t\t<p><strong>Image of <span class=\"customMeta\" data-dictid=\"415c59955f16927771947b9c105bbf\">ophthalmoscope</span> </strong></p>\n\t\t\t</td>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"border-color:#000000; border-style:solid; border-width:1px; text-align:center; vertical-align:top\"><img alt=\"\" data-author=\"\" data-hash=\"\" data-license=\"\" data-source=\"\" data-tags=\"\" height=\"1600\" src=\"https://image.prepladder.com/content/xaFsHF03IYHMQsLkoT8s1741023721.png\" width=\"629\" /></td>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"border-color:#000000; border-style:solid; border-width:1px; text-align:center; vertical-align:top\"><img alt=\"\" data-author=\"\" data-hash=\"\" data-license=\"\" data-source=\"\" data-tags=\"\" height=\"1480\" src=\"https://image.prepladder.com/content/y5lmzjZP1vA2Qbty0MYk1741023727.png\" width=\"1600\" /></td>\n\t\t</tr>\n\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid #000000; border-left:1px solid #000000; border-right:1px solid #000000; border-top:1px solid #000000; vertical-align:top\">\n\t\t\t<p><strong>Image Characteristics</strong></p>\n\t\t\t</td>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid #000000; border-left:1px solid #000000; border-right:1px solid #000000; border-top:1px solid #000000; vertical-align:top\">\n\t\t\t<p><strong>Erect, virtual</strong></p>\n\t\t\t</td>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid #000000; border-left:1px solid #000000; border-right:1px solid #000000; border-top:1px solid #000000; vertical-align:top\">\n\t\t\t<p>Real, inverted</p>\n\t\t\t</td>\n\t\t</tr>\n\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid #000000; border-left:1px solid #000000; border-right:1px solid #000000; border-top:1px solid #000000; vertical-align:top\">\n\t\t\t<p><strong>Magnification</strong></p>\n\t\t\t</td>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid #000000; border-left:1px solid #000000; border-right:1px solid #000000; border-top:1px solid #000000; vertical-align:top\">\n\t\t\t<p>About 15x (more in myopes, less in hypermetropes)</p>\n\t\t\t</td>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid #000000; border-left:1px solid #000000; border-right:1px solid #000000; border-top:1px solid #000000; vertical-align:top\">\n\t\t\t<p>About 2.5x with a +20D lens, smaller with stronger lenses</p>\n\t\t\t</td>\n\t\t</tr>\n\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid #000000; border-left:1px solid #000000; border-right:1px solid #000000; border-top:1px solid #000000; vertical-align:top\">\n\t\t\t<p><strong>Field of View</strong></p>\n\t\t\t</td>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid #000000; border-left:1px solid #000000; border-right:1px solid #000000; border-top:1px solid #000000; vertical-align:top\">\n\t\t\t<p>Limited, detailed central <span class=\"customMeta\" data-dictid=\"f17d8978bd1692777197621051012f\">retina</span> examination</p>\n\t\t\t</td>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid #000000; border-left:1px solid #000000; border-right:1px solid #000000; border-top:1px solid #000000; vertical-align:top\">\n\t\t\t<p>Larger field of view</p>\n\t\t\t</td>\n\t\t</tr>\n\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid #000000; border-left:1px solid #000000; border-right:1px solid #000000; border-top:1px solid #000000; vertical-align:top\">\n\t\t\t<p><strong>Uses</strong></p>\n\t\t\t</td>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid #000000; border-left:1px solid #000000; border-right:1px solid #000000; border-top:1px solid #000000; vertical-align:top\">\n\t\t\t<p><strong>Routine <span class=\"customMeta\" data-dictid=\"67492c42be16927772039f6e37110e\">fundus</span> examination</strong></p>\n\t\t\t</td>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid #000000; border-left:1px solid #000000; border-right:1px solid #000000; border-top:1px solid #000000; vertical-align:top\">\n\t\t\t<p>Essential for assessing <span class=\"customMeta\" data-dictid=\"fb7a2c30e416927771972f7df6f8c0\">retinal</span> <span class=\"customMeta\" data-dictid=\"2b005085881692777186cf95c3ad51\">detachment</span> and <span class=\"customMeta\" data-dictid=\"255674f3271692777195c172d86daf\">peripheral</span> <span class=\"customMeta\" data-dictid=\"fb7a2c30e416927771972f7df6f8c0\">retinal</span> lesions</p>\n\t\t\t</td>\n\t\t</tr>\n\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid #000000; border-left:1px solid #000000; border-right:1px solid #000000; border-top:1px solid #000000; vertical-align:top\">\n\t\t\t<p><strong>Prerequisites</strong></p>\n\t\t\t</td>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid #000000; border-left:1px solid #000000; border-right:1px solid #000000; border-top:1px solid #000000; vertical-align:top\">\n\t\t\t<p><strong>Semi-darkroom</strong></p>\n\t\t\t</td>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid #000000; border-left:1px solid #000000; border-right:1px solid #000000; border-top:1px solid #000000; vertical-align:top\">\n\t\t\t<p>Darkroom, dilated pupils, <span class=\"customMeta\" data-dictid=\"00ab88c6091692777185ea2685fa40\">convex</span> lens (+20D), <span class=\"customMeta\" data-dictid=\"eadd1d717a16927771833964224058\">binocular</span> ophthalmoscope</p>\n\t\t\t</td>\n\t\t</tr>\n\t</tbody>\n</table>\n\n<p> </p>",
