    {
      "text": "Identify the instrument used for handling delicate tissues during eye surgery.",
      "choices": [
        {
          "id": 0,
          "text": "Mcpherson forceps"
        },
        {
          "id": 1,
          "text": "Lim's forceps"
        },
        {
          "id": 2,
          "text": "Artery forceps"
        },
        {
          "id": 3,
          "text": "SR holding forceps"
        }
      ],
      "correct_choice_id": 1,
      "solution": "<p><strong>Correct Answer: B) Lims forceps</strong></p>\n\n<p><strong>Explanation:</strong></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img alt=\"Lim's forceps\" data-author=\"\" data-hash=\"12985\" data-license=\"\" data-source=\"\" data-tags=\"May2025\" height=\"222\" src=\"https://image.prepladder.com/notes/EDglthTC0tBAfKDvGaAo1747656117.png\" width=\"400\" /></p>\n\n<ul>\n\t<li>The instrument in the given image is Lims forceps</li>\n\t<li>It is used to hold the <span class=\"customMeta\" data-dictid=\"4cc4d657841692777185555e1b982d\">cornea</span> or <span class=\"customMeta\" data-dictid=\"3e4400809d16927771983252fc08b1\">sclera</span> edge for suturing during surgery</li>\n</ul>\n\n<p><strong>Mcpherson <span class=\"customMeta\" data-dictid=\"c01b366a9c1692777203ef77069d2c\">forceps</span> (Option A) </strong>Its use it to provide an <span class=\"customMeta\" data-dictid=\"a1b06f401f1692777182916497ccc6\">atraumatic</span> way to hold, <span class=\"customMeta\" data-dictid=\"07878e8260169277719971eb6eb629\">stitch</span> and retract tissues during <span class=\"customMeta\" data-dictid=\"781e6a5a991692777183252720baad\">cataract</span> or <span class=\"customMeta\" data-dictid=\"61e49875801692777188ad5edea804\">glaucoma</span> surgeries</p>\n\n<p><strong>Artery <span class=\"customMeta\" data-dictid=\"c01b366a9c1692777203ef77069d2c\">forceps</span> (Option C) </strong>It is used to control <span class=\"customMeta\" data-dictid=\"41e858bf2816927771836d46c619b9\">bleeding</span> from blood vessels by <span class=\"customMeta\" data-dictid=\"af0a383919169277718458bbb97b6b\">clamping</span> the artery</p>\n\n<p><strong>SR holding <span class=\"customMeta\" data-dictid=\"c01b366a9c1692777203ef77069d2c\">forceps</span> (Option D) </strong>It is used to stabilize the <span class=\"customMeta\" data-dictid=\"53c6bebcbb169277718777b3fe0e5c\">eyeball</span> during <span class=\"customMeta\" data-dictid=\"781e6a5a991692777183252720baad\">cataract</span> surgery</p>",
      "question_images": [
        "https://image.prepladder.com/notes/EDglthTC0tBAfKDvGaAo1747656117.png"
      ],
      "explanation_video": null,
      "explanation_images": [
        "https://image.prepladder.com/notes/EDglthTC0tBAfKDvGaAo1747656117.png"
      ],
